01:04:25,880 --> 01:04:27,916
- I'm bagging. Sir! Sir!
- Izzi! Lzzi!

502
01:04:28,000 --> 01:04:30,798
- Get the family out. Get him out!
- Sir, please!

503
01:04:30,880 --> 01:04:32,199
- Pads.
- Charging.

504
01:04:32,280 --> 01:04:33,235
- Pulse?
- Thready.

505
01:04:33,320 --> 01:04:34,514
Pressure?

506
01:04:38,600 --> 01:04:40,511
Oh, God.

507
01:05:01,000 --> 01:05:02,638
Tommy.

508
01:05:04,440 --> 01:05:06,476
I know. I know.

509
01:05:06,560 --> 01:05:09,199
I've never seen anything like it.

510
